Figure 4A

#This section calculates the signature score for neutrophils and adds the
#score to the object metadata
neutrophil_features <- c("S100A9", "S100A8", "CSF3R", "MSRB1", "CCRL2")
counts <- ileal.involved.post@assays$RNA@counts 
counts_df <- as.data.frame(counts)
gene_metadata_neutrophil <- as.data.frame(cbind(rownames(counts_df), rowMeans(counts_df), rowSums(!counts_df == 0)/dim(counts_df)[2]))
gene_metadata_neutrophil$V1 <- NULL
colnames(gene_metadata_neutrophil) <- c("mean_expression", "detection_freq")
gene_index_neutrophil <- match(neutrophil_features, rownames(gene_metadata_neutrophil))

gene_index_neutrophil <- gene_index_neutrophil[!is.na(gene_index_neutrophil)]
feature_df <- gene_metadata_neutrophil[gene_index_neutrophil,]
other_df <- gene_metadata_neutrophil[-gene_index_neutrophil,]

neutrophil.gene <- nn2(other_df, feature_df, k = 10)
neutrophil.gene.index <- unique(as.vector(neutrophil.gene$nn.idx))
neutrophil.gene.df <- other_df[neutrophil.gene.index,]

neutrophil.index <- match(rownames(neutrophil.gene.df), rownames(counts_df))
neutrophil.sig.df <- counts_df[gene_index_neutrophil, ]
neutrophil.df <- counts_df[neutrophil.index,]
sig.score <- colMeans(neutrophil.sig.df) - colMeans(neutrophil.df)

ileal.involved.post@meta.data$"neutrophil.sig"<- sig.score

#This section visualizes the signature score on the umapplot
FeaturePlot(object = ileal.involved.post, 
            features = "neutrophil.sig",
            order = TRUE,
            min.cutoff = 'q10', 
            label = FALSE,
            repel = TRUE)

#the signature score in the metadata

counts <- ileal.involved.post@assays$RNA@counts 
counts_df <- as.data.frame(counts)
gene_metadata <- as.data.frame(cbind(rownames(counts_df), rowMeans(counts_df), rowSums(!counts_df == 0)/dim(counts_df)[2]))
gene_metadata$V1 <- NULL
colnames(gene_metadata) <- c("mean_expression", "detection_freq")

gene_index <- match(features, rownames(gene_metadata))
gene_index <- gene_index[!is.na(gene_index)]
feature_df <- gene_metadata[gene_index,]
other_df <- gene_metadata[-gene_index,]

bg.gene <- nn2(other_df, feature_df, k = 10)
bg.gene.index <- unique(as.vector(bg.gene$nn.idx))
bg.gene.df <- other_df[bg.gene.index,]

bg.index <- match(rownames(bg.gene.df), rownames(counts_df))
sig.df <- counts_df[gene_index, ]
bg.df <- counts_df[bg.index,]
sig.score <- colMeans(sig.df) - colMeans(bg.df)
ileal.involved.post@meta.data$"mTOR_leading_edge_sig_score"<- sig.score

FeaturePlot(object = ileal.involved.post, 
            features = "mTOR_leading_edge_sig_score",
            order = TRUE,
            min.cutoff = 'q10',

            repel = TRUE)
